 outlets overhauling stockcontrol and orderingsystems and selling a palatial office in milan in order to move guccis headquarters back to florence second he had the more difficult task of making the gucci name desirable in the marketplace once more in this regard he decided that the company should become a modern fashion house rather than continuing to concentrate on classics such as loafer shoes decorated with a horses bit first made in  or handbags with bent bamboo handles produced since  de sole then handed over creative control to tom ford an american designer and the latters use of vivid satin and deep velvet was the success  page  of  next  more on domenico de sole guccis savior loading apa     mla     chicago domenico de sole guccis savior  december  in lotsofessayscom retrieved  july   from httpswwwcollegetermpaperscomviewpaperhtml lots of essays domenico de sole guccis savior lotsofessayscom lotsofessayscom december   web  jul  lots of essays domenico de sole guccis savior lotsofessayscom httpswwwcollegetermpaperscomviewpaperhtml accessed july     home  join  faqs  support  acceptable use policy copyright     collegetermpaperscom all rights reserved dmca